amenu &txt2tags.Settings.Target.xhtml                  <Esc><Esc>a%!target: xhtml<CR>
imenu &txt2tags.Settings.Target.xhtml                  <Esc><Esc>a%!target: xhtml<CR>
amenu &txt2tags.Settings.Target.tex                    <Esc><Esc>a%!target: tex<CR>
